I'm sorry. It's sold out.

352
00:30:18,583 --> 00:30:21,119
Then... I'll have Eisbein.

353
00:30:21,687 --> 00:30:23,121
Eisbein...

354
00:30:24,823 --> 00:30:26,491
I'll tell you a secret.

355
00:30:26,558 --> 00:30:28,393
The Eisbein in our restaurant
is disgusting.

356
00:30:32,531 --> 00:30:34,433
Then what do you recommend?

357
00:30:35,701 --> 00:30:37,869
How about our "Chef's Favorite"?

358
00:30:37,936 --> 00:30:40,138
-Okay.
-Okay, one moment please.

359
00:30:44,376 --> 00:30:45,744
Excuse me.

360
00:30:48,046 --> 00:30:49,114
It's so pretty.

361
00:30:50,716 --> 00:30:51,550
