366
00:31:09,401 --> 00:31:10,235
Please wait one moment.

367
00:31:15,674 --> 00:31:17,075
Did you call for me, miss?

368
00:31:20,979 --> 00:31:24,516
A handsome and talented chef as expected.

369
00:31:25,584 --> 00:31:26,418
Miss.

370
00:31:27,419 --> 00:31:30,722
Well, can I ask our handsome
and talented chef a question?

371
00:31:31,857 --> 00:31:35,427
How did you come up with
this romantic and pretty dish?

372
00:31:37,262 --> 00:31:39,431
This is a long story. Can I sit here?

373
00:31:39,498 --> 00:31:40,365
Yes.

374
00:31:43,235 --> 00:31:44,069
Thank you.

375
00:32:03,288 --> 00:32:04,723
Today is a special day.

376
00:32:07,559 --> 00:32:09,995
I earned my first salary.

377
00:32:14,733 --> 00:32:16,001
The feeling is so special.

378
00:32:18,837 --> 00:32:19,704
I'm very happy.

379
00:32:21,506 --> 00:32:22,374
I'm very excited.

380
00:32:25,210 --> 00:32:26,278
And very touched.

381
00:32:29,581 --> 00:32:34,953
So... I thought of the person
who's been very important to me.

382
00:32:39,024 --> 00:32:40,358
She gave me a second life.

383
00:32:43,128 --> 00:32:48,567
She protected me from a knife
and she saved me.

384
00:32:52,404 --> 00:32:55,207
She could've left me alone in my sad past.

385
00:32:59,611 --> 00:33:05,684
But instead, she chose
to waste her life with me.

386
00:33:11,156 --> 00:33:13,124
I don't know how to thank her.

387
00:33:16,161 --> 00:33:18,997
I haven't even cooked for her.

388
00:33:21,566 --> 00:33:23,401
So I...

389
00:33:33,178 --> 00:33:36,047
Did Da Xin teach you this speech, too?

390
00:33:38,817 --> 00:33:39,684
No.

391
00:33:42,320 --> 00:33:43,722
Then you should say it again later.

392
00:33:43,955 --> 00:33:45,023
I want to memorize it.

393
00:33:54,900 --> 00:33:55,767
What for?

394
00:33:56,468 --> 00:33:57,736
Let's dance before eating.

395
00:34:01,273 --> 00:34:02,674
I can't dance.

396
00:34:04,175 --> 00:34:06,244
Didn't you just say
you wanted to thank me?

397
00:34:06,878 --> 00:34:09,481
You should do whatever I tell you to do.

398
00:34:09,814 --> 00:34:11,616
I've already cooked spaghetti for you.

399
00:34:11,683 --> 00:34:12,550
What else do you want?

400
00:34:13,451 --> 00:34:14,419
I want to dance.

401
00:34:18,490 --> 00:34:19,424
You'll regret it.

402
00:34:19,491 --> 00:34:20,325
No.

403
00:34:20,659 --> 00:34:21,493
Come on.

404
00:34:21,559 --> 00:34:23,094
Then you can't laugh.

405
00:34:23,161 --> 00:34:25,230
Don't worry. I'll laugh behind your back.

406
00:34:36,541 --> 00:34:37,475
Do you like it?

407
00:34:38,076 --> 00:34:39,244
A nice bow tie, right?

408
00:34:39,311 --> 00:34:40,745
It's so cute.

409
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:43,481
I spent a whole night making it.

410
00:34:43,748 --> 00:34:45,050
Show some respect, okay?

411
00:35:25,090 --> 00:35:27,525
<i>My dear friends, the rain is coming.</i>

412
00:35:27,926 --> 00:35:30,028
<i>It's called "The Valentine's Day Rain".</i>

413
00:35:30,095 --> 00:35:32,464
<i>Why is it always raining
at Valentine's Day?</i>

414
00:35:32,530 --> 00:35:35,100
<i>Why is god such a killjoy?</i>

415
00:35:35,433 --> 00:35:38,670
<i>I think there must be a reason for this.</i>

416
00:35:38,737 --> 00:35:41,439
<i>Everyone is holding
their umbrella in the rain.</i>

417
00:35:41,506 --> 00:35:45,343
<i>Maybe there are so many new relationships
under those umbrellas.</i>

418
00:35:45,944 --> 00:35:47,512
Let's see this fax.

419
00:35:48,113 --> 00:35:50,248
This fax is from Xiaoting in Xindian.

420
00:35:51,149 --> 00:35:54,552
<i>Xiaoting wants to tell Ah Ping
the following words.</i>

421
00:35:54,853 --> 00:35:59,591
<i>I've liked you for a long time
but you never knew.</i>

422
00:35:59,658 --> 00:36:02,761
<i>Please turn around
and notice me, will you?</i>

423
00:36:03,895 --> 00:36:07,032
I believe, Ah Ping, you're always
looking straight ahead.

424
00:36:07,098 --> 00:36:09,868
But you'll never look beside you.

425
00:36:09,934 --> 00:36:13,638
In fact, the best things
and people are beside you.

426
00:36:15,073 --> 00:36:19,177
I hope all the friends
who want to show their loves,

427
00:36:19,244 --> 00:36:24,916
who want to apologize, and who want
to break up, fax me. I'm waiting for you.

428
00:36:26,317 --> 00:36:27,452
Shancai.

429
00:36:29,521 --> 00:36:31,656
Get in the car, come on.

430
00:36:31,890 --> 00:36:32,924
Quick.

431
00:36:34,092 --> 00:36:35,493
It's a good thing I'm here, right?

432
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:36,961
How did you know I was here?

433
00:36:37,028 --> 00:36:38,730
I knew when you would get off work.

434
00:36:38,797 --> 00:36:40,999
I was late and there was this rain.

435
00:36:41,066 --> 00:36:43,468
I thought you would take shelter
from the rain without your umbrella.

436
00:36:43,635 --> 00:36:45,036
So I was driving around looking for you.

437
00:36:45,537 --> 00:36:46,838
What did you say?

438
00:36:46,905 --> 00:36:49,074
Why did you turn the radio so high?

439
00:36:51,943 --> 00:36:55,046
Nothing. I won't hear it
if I turn it down.

440
00:36:55,447 --> 00:36:56,514
What's wrong with your ears?

441
00:36:58,116 --> 00:36:59,517
Nothing... Nothing.

442
00:37:00,785 --> 00:37:02,053
Qinghe, what's the matter?

443
00:37:02,120 --> 00:37:03,188
Why are you so nervously?

444
00:37:04,222 --> 00:37:05,523
Yeah, why am I so nervous?

445
00:37:08,326 --> 00:37:14,332
Most requests are songs
for lovers to express how they feel.

446
00:37:14,399 --> 00:37:18,103
Every listener thinks
their love is the most special one.

447
00:37:18,737 --> 00:37:22,373
But I think relationships
aren't any different.

448
00:37:23,007 --> 00:37:29,781
But today I received a very special fax
that I want to share with you after ads.

449
00:37:36,387 --> 00:37:37,455
Here we go...

450
00:37:38,056 --> 00:37:39,090
What?

451
00:37:39,858 --> 00:37:42,026
Nothing. Shancai,
I'm want to drink a soda.

452
00:37:42,093 --> 00:37:43,228
Wait for me here, be right back.

453
00:37:43,294 --> 00:37:44,863
<i>A very special fax...</i>

454
00:37:44,929 --> 00:37:47,265
-Qinghe!
<i>-from Qinghe in Taipei.</i>

455
00:37:47,332 --> 00:37:50,335
<i>Qinghe hopes Shancai
can stay like Shancai forever.</i>

456
00:37:51,169 --> 00:37:53,271
<i>Isn't it special?</i>

457
00:37:53,338 --> 00:37:59,978
<i>Qinghe wants to tell Shancai,
"Do you remember, in the first grade,</i>

458
00:38:00,044 --> 00:38:02,213
<i>Once, I failed my math exam.</i>

459
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:06,384
<i>The teacher said,
I'll beat your hand for every mistake.</i>

460
00:38:06,451 --> 00:38:08,353
<i>I got 24 mistakes.</i>

461
00:38:08,686 --> 00:38:11,389
<i>I was shivering in my seat.</i>

462
00:38:11,456 --> 00:38:14,526
<i>When the teacher called me
I almost passed out.</i>

463
00:38:15,460 --> 00:38:21,499
<i>Shancai, you raised up your hand, and told
the teacher to have half the punishment.</i>

464
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:23,802
<i>Our teacher asked why.</i>

465
00:38:23,868 --> 00:38:26,971
<i>You said you didn't teach me enough.</i>

466
00:38:27,038 --> 00:38:30,175
<i>So you had half the responsibility
when I failed.</i>

467
00:38:30,842 --> 00:38:37,415
<i>I will always remember that afternoon
in which you shared half my punishment.</i>

468
00:38:39,150 --> 00:38:44,189
<i>Shancai, I hope I can share
half your sorrow now.</i>

469
00:38:45,623 --> 00:38:49,828
I hope I can share half of your sadness.

470
00:38:49,894 --> 00:38:55,633
I hope that my Shancai, my good friend,
can find real happiness.

471
00:38:56,334 --> 00:38:58,670
Your friend forever, Qinghe."

472
00:38:59,704 --> 00:39:01,773
Shancai, did you know

473
00:39:02,273 --> 00:39:05,743
Qinghe recorded this song for you.

474
00:39:06,311 --> 00:39:07,712
"Close to You"

475
00:39:08,112 --> 00:39:14,252
<i>Why do birds suddenly appear</i>

476
00:39:14,319 --> 00:39:20,091
<i>Every time you are near?</i>

477
00:39:20,158 --> 00:39:25,530
<i>Just like me, they long to be</i>

478
00:39:25,597 --> 00:39:28,900
<i>Close to you</i>

479
00:39:31,002 --> 00:39:37,542
<i>Why do stars fall down from the sky</i>

480
00:39:37,609 --> 00:39:43,181
<i>Every time you walk by?</i>

481
00:39:43,248 --> 00:39:48,653
<i>Just like me, they long to be</i>

482
00:39:48,720 --> 00:39:52,523
<i>Close to you</i>

483
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:56,828
Qinghe.

484
00:39:56,895 --> 00:39:58,029
What are you doing?

485
00:40:00,565 --> 00:40:01,499
Get in.

486
00:40:20,285 --> 00:40:21,152
Thanks.

487
00:40:28,226 --> 00:40:29,193
For what?

488
00:40:29,961 --> 00:40:30,962
F3 was right.

489
00:40:31,029 --> 00:40:32,530
This was a bad idea.

490
00:40:32,597 --> 00:40:33,698
I wanted to make you happy.

491
00:40:34,299 --> 00:40:35,733
And now you are crying.

492
00:40:40,138 --> 00:40:42,507
I'm crying because I'm happy.

493
00:40:44,075 --> 00:40:46,144
<i>We don't pick up audience calls.</i>

494
00:40:46,210 --> 00:40:47,812
We'll make an exception today.

495
00:40:48,513 --> 00:40:49,847
Hello.

496
00:40:50,615 --> 00:40:51,449
Shancai.

497
00:40:52,250 --> 00:40:54,619
<i>You know I'm not good at this stuff.</i>

498
00:40:55,119 --> 00:40:57,689
<i>But Qinghe is right this time.</i>

499
00:40:59,924 --> 00:41:01,426
I think he's right.

500
00:41:01,492 --> 00:41:02,660
You should express your concern.

501
00:41:03,995 --> 00:41:05,563
<i>So I'm telling you,</i>

502
00:41:05,630 --> 00:41:07,031
<i>You're really ugly when you cry.</i>

503
00:41:08,666 --> 00:41:10,568
<i>You're somewhat pretty
when you're smiling.</i>

504
00:41:11,469 --> 00:41:12,971
So you know what to do.

505
00:41:13,037 --> 00:41:15,340
Cry less, smile more.

506
00:41:17,075 --> 00:41:17,942
That's it.

507
00:41:18,009 --> 00:41:18,977
Happy Valentine's Day.

508
00:41:19,043 --> 00:41:19,877
Goodbye.

509
00:41:22,847 --> 00:41:23,748
<i>Deep fried Shancai!</i>

510
00:41:24,816 --> 00:41:25,683
Meizuo.

511
00:41:26,050 --> 00:41:27,051
<i>I'm rooting for you.</i>

512
00:41:27,652 --> 00:41:29,120
Stay strong.

513
00:41:30,688 --> 00:41:33,091
<i>Shancai, stay strong.</i>

514
00:41:33,157 --> 00:41:36,227
<i>There's another one. Hello.</i>

515
00:41:39,464 --> 00:41:41,132
<i>I'm Daoming Si.</i>

516
00:41:41,199 --> 00:41:44,702
<i>My topic is "My Wish".</i>

517
00:41:45,236 --> 00:41:49,941
<i>My wish is to protect dad, mom, sister,</i>

518
00:41:50,008 --> 00:41:52,710
<i>Ximen, Meizuo, and Lei.</i>

519
00:41:52,777 --> 00:41:55,113
<i>I'll protect my bride.</i>

520
00:41:55,179 --> 00:41:57,448
<i>I'll keep them away from bad guys.</i>

521
00:41:57,515 --> 00:41:59,584
<i>I won't let them be sad.</i>

522
00:41:59,650 --> 00:42:01,552
<i>So I'll grow up fast.</i>

523
00:42:02,053 --> 00:42:03,788
<i>This is my wish.</i>

